from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split

Oenc = OrdinalEncoder()
Oenc.fit(df[['Name', 'Genre', 'Platform', 'Publisher']])
df[['Name', 'Genre', 'Platform', 'Publisher']] = Oenc.fit_transform(df[['Name', 'Genre', 'Platform', 'Publisher']])

Y = df['Platform']
X = df.drop(columns='Platform')

X_train, X_test, Y_train, Y_test = train_test_split(X,Y, 
                                                    test_size=0.2, 
                                                    random_state=42)
